ent to the emergency room, they want me to stay off my feet for two weeks fo=
r an open sore on the underside of my foot. Why this matters is I=E2=80=99m d=
iabetic. I=E2=80=99ve already had an amputation and it=E2=80=99s important I=
 follow through. I=E2=80=99m able to return to rehab after that time to fini=
sh the remaining two weeks. I know the timing isn=E2=80=99t ideal, it was ta=
king longer than expected. I want to follow through and prove to you and the=
 court I=E2=80=99m committed to finishing rehab. I=E2=80=99m in a good place=
, I hope this email finds you well and I appreciate you working with me on t=
his. Let me know if there is anything I need to do. I need additional time.
>=20
> Sincerely,
>=20
> Jeffery Kerr
